Alexie Gilmore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexie_Gilmore 0 Alexie Gilmore (born December 11, 1976) is an American actress who starred in the short-lived (five weeks) television series New Amsterdam as Dr. Sara Dillane. She is featured in the 2008 movie Definitely, Maybe and co-starred in the 2008 movie Surfer, Dude. Alexie also played the part of Kelly in the 2013 film Willow Creek. She played Devon Atwood in three episodes of CSI: Cyber as the wife of character Elijah Mundo. Alexie's other credits include 90210 and Legends. Gilmore was born in Manhattan and moved to Tenafly, New Jersey, where she attended Tenafly High School. Gilmore attended Allentown College (now known as DeSales University) in Center Valley, Pennsylvania.
